{"tid":2130201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：死撐名字冇專利  爆咪姐偷名寫藍書 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-07-29T05:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T05:50:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1bb49155ce04e26ee4bd3a7624b84ac9c2e4fd5","tid":2130201,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:46:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/local/20200729/FQFFE56FJSA4OPDO6NMNPAZGPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FFQFFE56FJSA4OPDO6NMNPAZGPA%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6QbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=f0aa1877\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FFQFFE56FJSA4OPDO6NMNPAZGPA%2F&h=f8e1b03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/local/20200729/FQFFE56FJSA4OPDO6NMNPAZGPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：死撐名字冇專利 <br />\n爆咪姐偷名寫藍書 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sVTBpYgeJEk0t03M16kF111jcoY=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UBOZVJDRSUQYRNGFRWDMV4TMAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsVTBpYgeJEk0t03M16kF111jcoY%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUBOZVJDRSUQYRNGFRWDMV4TMAM.jpg&h=85d4e211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被指盜用名字，潘麗瓊話「名字不是任何人的專利」，死撐撞名純屬巧合。<br />\n<br />\n前日傳媒界爆出一件狸貓換太子事件，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SzdAk_ZxNN_PQVVI0c1SepuwU0w=/773x1031/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WP7FUOBWD4G7AKPDJE54UCYXRA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSzdAk_ZxNN_PQVVI0c1SepuwU0w%3D%2F773x1031%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWP7FUOBWD4G7AKPDJE54UCYXRA.gif&h=71cd15eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n潘麗瓊喺《香港顏色密碼》中撰寫文章，以「施嘉雯」為筆名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EAfNoXlB47Vh4zZJtUmXjAkeaSE=/1175x589/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PZ5A3ZICVY34XMY4Y64Z6WDSFM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEAfNoXlB47Vh4zZJtUmXjAkeaSE%3D%2F1175x589%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPZ5A3ZICVY34XMY4Y64Z6WDSFM.gif&h=f2fc743a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受害人施嘉雯喺fb撰文，質問是否「拋下一句名字不是任何人的專利，便可以無敵？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫受害人自行澄清<br />\n<br />\n潘麗瓊喺文中話筆名係佢起，又話「文壇上使用筆名很普遍，魯迅就是筆名」，話如果有誤會就澄清，仲講到「名字不是任何人的專利」，批評外界對此事語帶嘲諷、抹黑，甚至牽連同書其他作者，佢仲將個波踢畀江迅，話佢曾一度要求用真名，「但主編要求我其中一篇用筆名」。不過，之前江迅又同真‧施嘉雯話，係作者唔想用真名，究竟邊個先係真？<br />\n<br />\n真‧施嘉雯之後喺fb撰文，話原來佢搵過潘麗瓊傾「施嘉雯事件」，但爆咪姐唔肯認用咗「施嘉雯」個名，只叫施嘉雯自己澄清，真‧施嘉雯話如果唔係有傳媒同KOL幫佢出聲，潘麗瓊唔會自爆，質問係咪「任何人，也可以『被作者』，拋下一句『名字不是任何人的專利』，便可以無敵？」<br />\n<br />\n網民見到潘小姐「名字不是任何人的專利」呢個言論，都大感贊同，即刻用「潘麗瓊」呢個筆名講聲「結束一黨專政」！"},{"pid":"5a269360f133638482207c43df57cf2d4789fbf0","tid":2130201,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:50:42.000Z","msg":"即刻出文用鄭月娥嗌習大大死全家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}